  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1227841">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1227841/" class="title-link">穿越之陌上花</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1227841"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1868503/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1868503-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1868503/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Burning flame</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-10-24"
      class="main-meta">2007-10-24 11:02:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1227841_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一千六百年前的南京叫建康，是东晋的首都。东晋的皇帝名头虽响，权力却不大。偏安江南以来，就几乎没做过主，始终是几个权臣说了算，先是王导，接着是桓温，之后是谢安。现在常说王谢王谢，没有桓温的事，那是因为他老人家曾经试图篡权，是乱臣贼子，最后被谢安收拾了。所以呢...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1227841/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">15有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1227841_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1227841_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评17篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
